<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/client/views/css/auth/signin.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <title>L O G I N</title>
  </head>

  <body class="bg-light">
    <header>
      <div id="headerNotice">
        <div style="font-weight: bolder">개발, 테스트 전용 웹 사이트</div>
        <div style="font-weight: 200;">
          <br>현재 웹 사이트는 개발 및 테스트 용도로 사용되며, <br>회원가입 및 제공해주신 정보는 15일 후 자동 파기됩니다.
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <form method="POST" id="formAccounts">
      <div style="font-weight: bolder; font-size: 24px;">로그인</div>
      <div class="input-group">
        <input id="id" class="form-control" name="login_id" type="text" placeholder="I  D" required>
        <br>
      </div>
      <div class="input-group">
        <input id="pw" class="form-control" name="login_pw" type="password" placeholder="P  W" required>
        <br>
      </div>
      <div class="input-group">
        <button id="btnLogin" class="btn btn-success" type="submit">로 그 인</button>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label id="lbSaveAccount" for="ipSaveAccount">
          <input id="ipSaveAccount" type="checkbox">&nbsp;&nbsp;ID 저장
        </label>
      </div>
      <hr>
      <div>
        <a class="aFinds" href="/find/id">아이디 찾기</a>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;
        <a class="aFinds" href="/find/pw">비밀번호 찾기</a>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;
        <a class="aFinds" href="/signup">회원가입</a>
      </div>
    </form>

    <footer>
      &copy;SunHyisu.. (Website dedicated to development)
    </footer>
  </body>

</html>
